      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD REVOLVER (1) has a strong record this trip with three wins and three placings from eight starts. Below best last time at this track (25.66) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths sixth. Makes strong appeal on best. VISTA YTTRIUM (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 25.28 beating Panda Unleashed. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. One of main contenders. ARMATREE STRIPE (4) was a strong course and distance winner last time, claiming a Grade 5 in a speedy 24.95 and a new PB here. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. SHORTY (3) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
